{"id":231028,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/global-voices-肯尼亚：都市农艺生根/","date":"2012-06-13T13:56:28Z","modified":"2012-06-13T13:56:28Z","title":"Global Voices | 肯尼亚：都市农艺生根","content":"<p><p>肯尼亚的都市居民正学习各种不同方法，好在有限空间内种植可供食用并出售的食物。对低收入或没有收入的人来说，都市园艺可能是确保食物来源的关键。以下影片介绍如何利用有限的空间和资源在容器中种植食物。</p>\n<p>Mammut 制片的 Michele Mellara 的 Alessandro Rossi 拍摄的纪录片<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yo9I4zexUfg\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yo9I4zexUfg\">天佑绿叶</a>，其中关于袋中农园的片段描述奈洛比的都市园丁怎样利用垂直空间，在一平方公尺中种出足够六口之家食用的菜叶：</p>\n<p> </p>\n</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/Beablessingtoday?feature=watch\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/Beablessingtoday?feature=watch\">Be a Blessing Today</a> 上传了一系列的影片，由他在肯尼亚的菜园中示范不同的都市耕种技巧。其中之一正是前面提到的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ezoCxMsMZ88\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ezoCxMsMZ88\">袋耕法</a>，经过改良让灌溉更简易：</p>\n</p>\n<p>他所示范的另外两种技巧是<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GNdInHRt0Q4\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GNdInHRt0Q4\">高台墙耕法</a>，利用加高的墙型土台种植就不需要弯下腰耕种收割；<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x0djlwKOWQs\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x0djlwKOWQs\">阶梯耕法</a>则可以在铺设水泥的区域栽种蔬菜。这些都是利用空间让耕种更简便的方法。</p>\n</p>\n<p>Youtube 上也有来自世界各地的人分享在有限空间中耕种的技巧。比如这是用不要的塑胶瓶打造立体菜园的好方法：</p>\n</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q2OVIXK6TwI\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q2OVIXK6TwI\">这段影片</a>示范如何在塑胶瓶改造的容器上下方种植植物：</p>\n</p>\n<p>另外这段<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f162GR7LPi4\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f162GR7LPi4\">影片</a>示范废轮胎也可以用来当作种菜的容器：</p>\n</p>\n<p><small>苗的图片来自<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/chrisseee/4465433814/in/photostream/\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/chrisseee/4465433814/in/photostream/\">Flickr的Chrisseee</a>，依据<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/deed.en\" href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/deed.en\">创用CC授权</a>使用。</small></p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E8%82%AF%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E9%83%BD%E5%B8%82%E5%86%9C%E8%89%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%B9&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11105%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11105%2F&#038;desc=%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E9%83%BD%E5%B8%82%E5%86%9C%E8%89%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%B9\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11105%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11105%2F&#038;text=%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E9%83%BD%E5%B8%82%E5%86%9C%E8%89%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%B9&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11105%2F&#038;title=%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E9%83%BD%E5%B8%82%E5%86%9C%E8%89%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%B9\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F06%2F13%2F11105%2F&#038;title=%E8%82%AF%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%EF%BC%9A%E9%83%BD%E5%B8%82%E5%86%9C%E8%89%BA%E7%94%9F%E6%A0%B9\" title=\"StumbleUpon\"><span>StumbleUpon</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofo